<plot>When Zen, former girlfriend of a Thai mob boss, falls for Masashi, a Japanese gangster in Thailand, the boss banishes them: Masashi to Japan, and Zen, with her small daughter Zin, to live next to a martial arts school. Zin is autistic, with uncanny swift reflexes. She watches the students next door and Kung Fu movies, absorbing every technique. She's now a teen, and her mother needs chemotherapy. Zen has taken in a chubby kid, Moom, who watches over Zin. Moom finds a ledger listing business men who owe Zen money; he goes to them one at a time to collect in order to pay for Zen's treatment. Zin, with her martial skills, becomes his enforcer. A showdown with the boss is inevitable.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?104174</url></doc>
